OL,3,C'I don't sleep anymore': Mum of
OL,4,Cholidaymaker missing in Sardinia
OL,6,FThe mother of a Somerset man who went
OL,7,Fmissing in Sardinia six months ago has
OL,8,Fspoken of her anguish as the
OL,9,Finvestigation into his disappearance
OL,10,Fcontinues.
OL,12,FCristina Pittalis' son Michael Frison,
OL,13,Ffrom Chard, went missing while
OL,14,Fvisiting the Italian island in July.
OL,16,FThe 25-year-old had gone to see his
OL,17,Fgrandparents, and travelled to the
OL,18,Fremote Luras region on July 12th.
OL,20,FThe following day, he went for a walk
OL,21,Fand has not been seen since.
