OL,3,C'I don't sleep anymore': Mum of
OL,4,Cholidaymaker missing in Sardinia
OL,6,F"I don't sleep anymore," Cristina told
OL,7,FITV News West Country.
OL,9,F"If I manage to have some sleep, I
OL,10,Fwake up in a panic. I have nightmares.
OL,11,FI miss Michael constantly - it's
OL,12,Falways on my mind."
OL,14,FWhile in Sardinia, Michael met up with
OL,15,Fa friend he had met online.
OL,17,FThe friend, called Niomi, assisted
OL,18,FItalian authorities with their search
OL,19,Fand investigation at the time but has
OL,20,Fsince left Sardinia.
