OL,3,C'I don't sleep anymore': Mum of
OL,4,Cholidaymaker missing in Sardinia
OL,6,F"Michael's brother and I were invited
OL,7,Fby many kind friends to spend the
OL,8,FChristmas with them (in Sardinia),"
OL,9,Fshe said.
OL,11,F"But we chose to stay home hoping for
OL,12,FMichael to knock on the door and come
OL,13,Fback - and that didn't happen.
OL,15,F"Let's not forget that Michael left
OL,16,Fall of his belongings, including his
OL,17,FID. Therefore, there is the hope that
OL,18,Fhe is still on the island. It is a big
OL,19,Fisland but it is not impossible to
OL,20,Fkeep looking for him."
